{"tid":1839642,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"白宮：特朗普已知武漢肺炎疫情  將避免在美擴散","createTime":"2020-01-24T13:45:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T02:30:04.000Z","uid":141151,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"bc720cd5f9744fb60f5100f44b4ea84accb14c8b","tid":1839642,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:45:30.000Z","msg":"白宮：特朗普已知武漢肺炎疫情將避免在美擴散<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.voachinese.com/a/white-house-wuhan-virus-20200124/5258537.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voachinese.com%2Fa%2Fwhite-house-wuhan-virus-20200124%2F5258537.html&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77dOJZs7QJHlESVJdSYWWwTM%3D&h=288d9bb2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.voachinese.com/a/white-house-wuhan-virus-20200124/5258537.html</a><br />\n<br />\n白宫 &mdash; <br />\n白宮官員表示，已經就武漢肺炎的疫情向特朗普總統簡報，並且將確保病情不會在美國擴散。<br />\n<br />\n中國武漢肺炎的疫情持續擴散，除了中國多個城市都發現病例，包括武漢等好幾個城市已經封城，病情也已經擴散到海外，包括日本、台灣、泰國等都發現病例，美國的華盛頓州也出現第一起病例。<br />\n<br />\n白宮副發言人吉德利（Hogan Gidley）1月23號星期四在白宮向記者表示，美國政府正在監控武漢肺炎的情勢發展，美國人民可以放心:&ldquo;美國人民可以對他們的安全感到放心，我們正在隨時監看局勢。總統已經聽取簡報，並且時刻保持警惕，確保病情不會散佈全國。我們已經向機場派出了更多人員。跟以往一樣，我們跟包括州層級以及聯邦層級，跟國土安全部、交通部，以及其他部門，進行相同程度的協調，來確保美國人民的安全。美國疾病控制與預防中心(CDC)領導這次任務，他們擁有所有的資訊，而他們持續進行監控。美國人民可以放心，我們已像過去那樣採取了一切必要的預防措施。我們將持續這樣做。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nCDC在1月20號啟動了&ldquo;緊急應變系統&rdquo;，來應對武漢肺炎對美國可能造成的影響。疾管局已經發展出及時的&ldquo;逆轉錄聚合酶鏈反應&rdquo;（Reverse Transcription-Polymerase Chain Reaction）測試，能夠檢測出俗稱武漢肺炎的&ldquo;2019新型冠狀病毒&rdquo;（2019-nCoV）。<br />\n<br />\nCDC此前宣佈在舊金山國際機場、紐約肯尼迪機場和洛杉磯國際機場對武漢旅客進行入境檢查，並且將在哈茨菲爾德-傑克遜亞特蘭大國際機場(ATL)和芝加哥奧黑爾國際機場(ORD)增設入境檢查。"},{"pid":"872005690929ddf7a254f771c71d248a777cd0a2","tid":1839642,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:47:57.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"869bb6f6a155dc24d33a3994b8b3b521ae713f1e","tid":1839642,"uid":313341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:48:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"68271328f3ce0f247a12dc3b3aaed43f04d125a9","tid":1839642,"uid":104138,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:48:29.000Z","msg":"Trump plz save Hong Kong<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"74554a8d58154af79a7e2686e51e69011a45f00c","tid":1839642,"uid":128118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:49:14.000Z","msg":"美帝幾時先肯出手清洗哂d蝗蟲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBtw幫推 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n11月8日大家悼念緊周梓樂同學既時候 呢班人竟然咁做 重上埋神枱<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">認清同路人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1839581\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1839581</a>"},{"pid":"da72fe0b6c63b26333f79a9eb74b1e56fa448526","tid":1839642,"uid":122275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:49:16.000Z","msg":"信美帝得永生"},{"pid":"4d31f1aa05be77daebb349e14c686007925e11ac","tid":1839642,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:52:27.000Z","msg":"直接 用 飛彈 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e84407e23e45173709151af103da60bb9a270bc9","tid":1839642,"uid":185126,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:53:45.000Z","msg":"侵侵不如向支那射幾十個核彈滅撚咗支那佢算啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"048d9d1a4a70d556793e7a2b27ded06ef25fad30","tid":1839642,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:18:22.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">CDC please save HK</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"093e1c7662491f8a050a8184ecd27574a215f1ab","tid":1839642,"uid":8858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:19:55.000Z","msg":"侵侵又有牌用，連任在望"},{"pid":"5e372209bc7754e2daadff0f76c332bb614195be","tid":1839642,"uid":57376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T00:38:45.000Z","msg":"CDC在1月20號啟動了&ldquo;緊急應變系統&rdquo;，來應對武漢肺炎對美國可能造成的影響。疾管局已經發展出及時的&ldquo;逆轉錄聚合酶鏈反應&rdquo;（Reverse Transcription-Polymerase Chain Reaction）測試，能夠檢測出俗稱武漢肺炎的&ldquo;2019新型冠狀病毒&rdquo;（2019-nCoV）。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好快手<br />\n可能一早知道支那製造緊生化武器"},{"pid":"b095739010dae84ce84bc03ce3b0f068145de6ab","tid":1839642,"uid":76776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T00:41:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"03f1199ec34d99310513c0636feba0811f085042","tid":1839642,"uid":46822,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T00:42:29.000Z","msg":"支那成日吹奏自己科技幾勁幾勁<br />\n今次病毒就見真章<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf80f3db7034ac23ea73a7c58a4d8a6e39805f2","tid":1839642,"uid":130105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"093e1c7662491f8a050a8184ecd27574a215f1ab","tid":1839642,"uid":8858,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T14:19:55.000Z","msg":"侵侵又有牌用，連任在望"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"20